üîπ Unicast, Broadcast, Multicast (Missing)
Unicast ‚Üí One-to-one
Broadcast ‚Üí One-to-all
Multicast ‚Üí One-to-group
Used heavily in streaming.

üîπ MTU & Fragmentation (Important)
MTU = 1500 bytes (Ethernet)
If packet > MTU ‚Üí Fragmentation at routers.

